---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About — Zurhaar Tools" description="About Andreas Zurhaar — AI engineer building tools to save you time.">
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-2xl">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6">About</h1>

      <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none">
        <p class="text-lg text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Hi, I'm Andreas Zurhaar — an AI engineer based in the Netherlands. I build tools that leverage AI to automate repetitive tasks and save people time.
        </p>

        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Zurhaar Tools is my growing catalog of browser extensions, scripts, and digital products. Each tool is designed to solve a specific problem — no bloat, no subscriptions you don't need, just tools that work.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-4">What I build</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-text-muted">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary font-bold mt-0.5">&#8227;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-text">Browser extensions</strong> — AI-powered Chrome extensions that work while you browse.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary font-bold mt-0.5">&#8227;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-text">Scripts & tools</strong> — Automation scripts and utilities that handle tedious work.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary font-bold mt-0.5">&#8227;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-text">Templates & resources</strong> — Ready-to-use prompt packs, Notion templates, and more.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-4">Get in touch</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          Have a question or suggestion? Reach out at
          <a href="mailto:andreas@zurhaartools.com" class="text-primary hover:text-primary-dark transition-colors">andreas@zurhaartools.com</a>
          or find me on
          <a href="https://github.com/andreaszurhaar" class="text-primary hover:text-primary-dark transition-colors">GitHub</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
